{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775848532643,"sessionID":"ses_2872fe219ffe8JUj26k1EB2YSq","part":{"id":"prt_d78d0f17d001DK5Oif1jASsgsE","messageID":"msg_d78d0d8a70018jMZM4BHObLQ4R","sessionID":"ses_2872fe219ffe8JUj26k1EB2YSq","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_abcdf9d4929d4deb8168c38f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-010 — Router 会话管理\n\n- **AR ID**: AR-010\n- **Module**: `pkg/router`\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Draft\n\n## 1. 概述\n\n`pkg/router` 是 agentcube 的 HTTP 反向代理核心模块，负责将外部 HTTP 请求路由到后端的 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 实例。本设计文档聚焦于**会话管理**（Session Management）功能，基于已有的反向代理能力，增加对会话生命周期、状态追踪、JWT 认证和动态服务发现的支持。\n\n### 1.1 目标\n\n- 实现基于 Kubernetes CRD 的动态后端服务发现\n- 支持会话生命周期管理（创建、更新、销毁）\n- 提供 JWT 令牌认证和授权\n- 集成 client-go 进行 Kubernetes API 交互\n- 提供可观测性（Prometheus 指标、健康检查）\n\n### 1.2 依赖\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` — Kubernetes typed client\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/informers` — Shared informer\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/listers` — Resource listers\n- `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes` — Kubernetes clientset\n\n---\n\n## 2. 架构设计\n\n### 2.1 整体架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                            Client Requests                               │\n└─────────────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                  │\n                                  ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         Router Server (pkg/router)                       │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐    │\n│  │  Auth       │→ │  Rate Limit │→ │  Route      │→ │   Proxy     │    │\n│  │  Middleware │  │  Middleware  │  │  Handler    │  │   Handler   │    │\n│  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘    │\n│         │                 │                │                │           │\n│  ┌──────▼─────────────────▼────────────────▼────────────────▼──────┐   │\n│  │                     Backend Pool Manager                         │   │\n│  └────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────┘   │\n└───────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                                │\n        ┌───────────────────────┼───────────────────────┐\n        │                       │                       │\n        ▼                       ▼                       ▼\n┌───────────────┐      ┌─────────────────┐     ┌────────────────┐\n│   Health      │      │   Kubernetes    │     │    Metrics     │\n│   Checker     │      │   Informer      │     │    Collector   │\n└───────────────┘      └────────┬────────┘     └────────────────┘\n                                │\n                                ▼\n                 ┌─────────────────────────────┐\n                 │   Kubernetes API Server    │\n                 │  ┌─────────────────────┐  │\n                 │  │ AgentRuntime CRs     │  │\n                 │  │ CodeInterpreter CRs │  │\n                 │  └─────────────────────┘  │\n                 └─────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n### 2.2 核心组件\n\n| 组件 | 职责 |\n|------|------|\n| `Router` | HTTP 服务器生命周期管理、主路由入口 |\n| `BackendPool` | 后端服务实例池管理、健康状态追踪 |\n| `RouteHandler` | 请求路径解析与目标后端选择 |\n| `ProxyHandler` | HTTP/WebSocket 请求转发 |\n| `HealthChecker` | 后端健康检查、故障检测 |\n| `Informer` | Kubernetes CRD 监听、动态服务发现 |\n| `Authenticator` | JWT/Bearer Token 认证 |\n| `RateLimiter` | 请求速率限制 |\n| `Metrics` | Prometheus 指标采集 |\n\n### 2.3 数据流\n\n```\n1. 客户端请求进入 Router\n   │\n2. Authenticator 验证认证信息 (JWT/Bearer)\n   │\n3. RateLimiter 检查速率限制\n   │\n4. RouteHandler 解析路径，提取 namespace/resource\n   │\n5. BackendPool 根据路径/Header 选择目标后端\n   │\n6. HealthChecker 检查后端健康状态\n   │\n7. ProxyHandler 转发请求到后端\n   │\n8. Metrics 记录请求指标\n   │\n9. 响应返回客户端\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3. 数据结构\n\n### 3.1 核心配置\n\n```go\n// Config holds router configuration\ntype Config struct {\n    // Server settings\n    ListenAddress       string        // Listen address (default: \":8080\")\n    BackendTimeout      time.Duration // Backend request timeout (default: 30s)\n    IdleTimeout         time.Duration // Idle connection timeout (default: 60s)\n\n    // Health check settings\n    HealthCheckInterval time.Duration // Health check interval (default: 10s)\n    HealthCheckTimeout  time.Duration // Health check timeout (default: 5s)\n    MaxFailures        int           // Max consecutive failures before marking unhealthy (default: 3)\n\n    // Connection pool settings\n    MaxConnsPerBackend  int           // Max connections per backend (default: 100)\n\n    // Rate limiting\n    RateLimitEnabled    bool          // Enable rate limiting (default: false)\n    RateLimitRPS        int           // Requests per second (default: 10)\n    RateLimitBurst      int           // Burst size (default: 20)\n\n    // Authentication\n    AuthEnabled         bool          // Enable authentication (default: false)\n    AuthToken           string        // Bearer token for auth\n\n    // Kubernetes integration\n    WatchNamespaces     []string      // Namespaces to watch (empty = all)\n    KubeConfigPath      string        // Path to kubeconfig (optional)\n    ResyncPeriod        time.Duration // Informer resync period (default: 30m)\n\n    // JWT settings\n    JWTEnabled         bool          // Enable JWT authentication (default: false)\n    JWTSecretName      string        // Kubernetes Secret name for JWT keys (default: \"agentcube-router-identity\")\n    JWTNamespace       string        // Secret namespace (default: \"default\")\n    JWTExpiration      time.Duration // Token expiration (default: 5m)\n}\n```\n\n### 3.2 后端服务\n\n```go\n// Backend represents a backend service instance\ntype Backend struct {\n    URL                 *url.URL      // Backend URL\n    PathPrefix          string        // Path prefix for routing\n    Name                string        // Backend name (for logging/metrics)\n    Healthy             bool          // Current health status\n    ConsecutiveFailures int           // Consecutive failure count\n    LastHealthyCheck    time.Time     // Last health check timestamp\n   mu                  sync.RWMutex   // Mutex for concurrent access\n}\n\n// BackendPool manages multiple backend instances\ntype BackendPool struct {\n    backends     map[string]*Backend   // key: \"agentruntime/namespace/name\" or \"codeinterpreter/namespace/name\"\n    headerRoutes map[string]map[string]string // header-based routing rules\n    defaultBackend string               // Default fallback backend\n    mu           sync.RWMutex\n}\n```\n\n### 3.3 代理上下文\n\n```go\n// ProxyContext holds request context for proxying\ntype ProxyContext struct {\n    Context     context.Context\n    Request     *http.Request\n    Response    http.ResponseWriter\n    Backend     *Backend\n    StartTime   time.Time\n    RequestID   string\n    Namespace   string\n    ResourceName string\n    ResourceKind string // \"agentruntime\" or \"codeinterpreter\"\n}\n```\n\n### 3.4 会话管理\n\n```go\n// SessionInfo represents session state\ntype SessionInfo struct {\n    SessionID     string            // Unique session identifier\n    Namespace     string            // Kubernetes namespace\n    ResourceName  string            // AgentRuntime/CodeInterpreter name\n    ResourceKind  string            // \"agentruntime\" or \"codeinterpreter\"\n    Endpoint      string            // Backend endpoint URL\n    CreatedAt     time.Time         // Session creation time\n    LastActivity  time.Time         // Last activity timestamp\n    ExpiresAt     time.Time         // Session expiration time\n    Labels        map[string]string // Labels from CR\n    Status        SessionStatus     // Current status\n}\n\n// SessionStatus enum\ntype SessionStatus string\n\nconst (\n    SessionStatusPending   SessionStatus = \"Pending\"\n    SessionStatusActive   SessionStatus = \"Active\"\n    SessionStatusIdle     SessionStatus = \"Idle\"\n    SessionStatusExpired  SessionStatus = \"Expired\"\n    SessionStatusFailed   SessionStatus = \"Failed\"\n)\n```\n\n### 3.5 JWT 管理\n\n```go\n// JWTManager handles JWT token generation and validation\ntype JWTManager struct {\n    privateKey     *rsa.PrivateKey\n    publicKey     *rsa.PublicKey\n    clientset     kubernetes.Interface\n    secretName    string\n    secretNamespace string\n    expiration    time.Duration\n}\n\n// JWT claims structure\ntype JWTClaims struct {\n    SessionID    string `json:\"session_id\"`\n    Namespace    string `json:\"namespace\"`\n    ResourceName string `json:\"resource_name\"`\n    ResourceKind string `json:\"resource_kind\"`\n    ExpiresAt    int64  `json:\"exp\"`\n    IssuedAt     int64  `json:\"iat\"`\n    Issuer       string `json:\"iss\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 4. API 合约\n\n### 4.1 HTTP 端点\n\n| Method | Path | Middleware | Handler |\n|--------|------|------------|---------|\n| GET | `/health/live` | none | `handleHealthLive` |\n| GET | `/health/ready` | none | `handleHealthReady` |\n| GET | `/metrics` | none | Prometheus metrics |\n| GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleAgentRuntimeProxy` |\n| POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleAgentRuntimeProxy` |\n| GET | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleCodeInterpreterProxy` |\n| POST | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/*path` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleCodeInterpreterProxy` |\n| WS | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/agent-runtimes/:name/ws` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleAgentRuntimeWS` |\n| WS | `/v1/namespaces/:namespace/code-interpreters/:name/ws` | auth, rateLimit, log | `handleCodeInterpreterWS` |\n\n### 4.2 代理请求头\n\n| Header | 描述 |\n|--------|------|\n| `X-Request-ID` | 请求唯一标识 |\n| `X-Forwarded-For` | 原始客户端 IP |\n| `X-Forwarded-Proto` | 原始协议 (http/https) |\n| `X-Real-IP` | 真实客户端 IP |\n| `X-Target-Namespace` | 目标 Kubernetes 命名空间 |\n| `X-Target-Name` | 目标资源名称 |\n| `X-Target-Kind` | 目标资源类型 (agentruntime/codeinterpreter) |\n| `X-Session-ID` | 会话标识 (JWT token 中的 session_id) |\n\n### 4.3 健康检查响应\n\n```go\n// Live check\n{\"status\": \"alive\"}\n\n// Ready check - OK\n{\"status\": \"ready\"}\n\n// Ready check - Not ready\n{\"status\": \"not ready\", \"error\": \"informers not synced\"}\n\n// Metrics endpoint\n# Prometheus metrics format\n```\n\n### 4.4 错误响应\n\n```json\n{\n  \"error\": \"error message\",\n  \"code\": \"ERR_CODE\",\n  \"requestId\": \"req-xxx\"\n}\n```\n\n| Status Code | Description |\n|-------------|-------------|\n| 200 | Success |\n| 400 | Bad Request (invalid path/params) |\n| 401 | Unauthorized (invalid/missing token) |\n| 404 | Resource not found |\n| 429 | Too Many Requests (rate limit) |\n| 502 | Bad Gateway (backend error) |\n| 503 | Service Unavailable (circuit open/overloaded) |\n| 504 | Gateway Timeout (backend timeout) |\n\n---\n\n## 5. Kubernetes 集成\n\n### 5.1 Informer 配置\n\n```go\n// NewSharedInformerFactory creates informer factory\nfunc NewSharedInformerFactory(client versioned.Interface, resyncPeriod time.Duration) externalversions.SharedInformerFactory\n\n// Watch AgentRuntime resources\nfactory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()\n\n// Watch CodeInterpreter resources\nfactory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()\n```\n\n### 5.2 事件处理\n\n```go\n// AgentRuntime event handlers\nfunc (i *Informer) AddAgentRuntime(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\nfunc (i *Informer) UpdateAgentRuntime(oldObj, newObj *agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\nfunc (i *Informer) DeleteAgentRuntime(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime)\n\n// CodeInterpreter event handlers\nfunc (i *Informer) AddCodeInterpreter(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter)\nfunc (i *Informer) UpdateCodeInterpreter(oldObj, newObj *agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter)\nfunc (i *Informer) DeleteCodeInterpreter(obj *agentcubev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter)\n```\n\n### 5.3 后端注册逻辑\n\n```\nAddAgentRuntime:\n  1. 检查 Status.Phase == \"Running\"\n  2. 检查 Status.Endpoint != \"\"\n  3. 构造 backend key: \"agentruntime/{namespace}/{name}\"\n  4. 从 Spec.TargetPorts 提取 PathPrefix (默认 \"/agent/\")\n  5. 调用 BackendPool.AddBackend()\n\nUpdateAgentRuntime:\n  1. 如果不再 Running 或无 Endpoint，调用 RemoveBackend()\n  2. 否则调用 BackendPool.UpdateBackend()\n\nDeleteAgentRuntime:\n  1. 调用 RemoveBackend()\n```\n\n---\n\n## 6. 错误处理\n\n### 6.1 错误类型\n\n```go\n// Error codes\nconst (\n    ErrCodeBadRequest       = \"ERR_BAD_REQUEST\"\n    ErrCodeNotFound         = \"ERR_NOT_FOUND\"\n    ErrCodeUnauthorized     = \"ERR_UNAUTHORIZED\"\n    ErrCodeTargetNotReady   = \"ERR_TARGET_NOT_READY\"\n    ErrCodeProxyFailed      = \"ERR_PROXY_FAILED\"\n    ErrCodeTimeout          = \"ERR_TIMEOUT\"\n    ErrCodeCircuitOpen      = \"ERR_CIRCUIT_OPEN\"\n    ErrCodeRateLimited      = \"ERR_RATE_LIMITED\"\n    ErrCodeInternalError    = \"ERR_INTERNAL\"\n)\n\n// RouterError represents a router-specific error\ntype RouterError struct {\n    Code       string\n    Message    string\n    StatusCode int\n    Err        error\n}\n```\n\n### 6.2 错误处理策略\n\n| 错误场景 | 处理策略 |\n|----------|----------|\n| 认证失败 | 返回 401，记录错误指标 |\n| 资源不存在 (404) | 返回 404，不重试 |\n| 速率超限 | 返回 429，提示客户端退避 |\n| 后端超时 | 记录失败，重试一次，失败则熔断 |\n| 后端连接失败 | 熔断计数，达到阈值后标记不健康 |\n| 熔断器开启 | 返回 503，定期尝试恢复 |\n| 内部错误 | 返回 500，记录错误日志 |\n\n### 6.3 日志规范\n\n```go\n// Structured logging with fields\nlog.Info(\"Request processed\",\n    \"requestId\", requestID,\n    \"method\", method,\n    \"path\", path,\n    \"namespace\", namespace,\n    \"resourceName\", resourceName,\n    \"backend\", backendName,\n    \"latency\", latency,\n    \"statusCode\", statusCode,\n)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 7. 测试策略\n\n### 7.1 单元测试\n\n| 模块 | 测试重点 |\n|------|----------|\n| `BackendPool` | 并发安全、路由选择、健康状态管理 |\n| `RouteHandler` | 路径解析、Header 路由、后端选择 |\n| `ProxyHandler` | URL 重写、Header 设置、连接池管理 |\n| `HealthChecker` | 健康检查触发、状态转换、失败计数 |\n| `Authenticator` | Token 验证、Middleware 流程 |\n| `RateLimiter` | 速率限制、并发安全、Middleware 流程 |\n| `Metrics` | 指标记录、标签正确性 |\n\n### 7.2 集成测试\n\n```go\n// 使用 fake client-go 进行集成测试\nimport (\n    \"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake\"\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned/fake\"\n)\n\nfunc TestRouterWithFakeClients(t *testing.T) {\n    // Setup fake clients\n    kubeClient := fake.NewSimpleClientset()\n    runtimeClient := clientsetfake.NewSimpleClientset()\n\n    // Create informer factory\n    informerFactory := externalversions.NewSharedInformerFactory(runtimeClient, 30*time.Minute)\n\n    // Create router with fake clients\n    router := NewRouter(&Config{\n        WatchNamespaces: []string{\"default\"},\n    })\n\n    // Add test AgentRuntime\n    ar := &agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n        ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n            Name:      \"test-runtime\",\n            Namespace: \"default\",\n        },\n        Status: agentcubev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeStatus{\n            Phase:    agentcubev1alpha1.PhaseRunning,\n            Endpoint: \"http://localhost:8081\",\n        },\n    }\n    runtimeClient.AgentRuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(context.Background(), ar, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n\n    // Start informers\n    informerFactory.Start(nil)\n    informerFactory.WaitForCacheSync(nil)\n\n    // Test proxy flow\n    req := httptest.NewRequest(\"GET\", \"/v1/namespaces/default/agent-runtimes/test-runtime/api\", nil)\n    w := httptest.NewRecorder()\n    router.ServeHTTP(w, req)\n\n    assert.Equal(t, http.StatusOK, w.Code)\n}\n```\n\n### 7.3 测试场景\n\n| 场景 | 预期结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| 正常代理流程 | 请求成功转发，后端响应正确返回 |\n| 后端动态添加 | Informer 事件触发，后端自动加入路由 |\n| 后端动态删除 | Informer 事件触发，后端从路由移除 |\n| 健康检查失败 | 连续失败 3 次后标记为不健康，流量切换 |\n| 认证失败 | 返回 401，请求不转发 |\n| 速率超限 | 返回 429，请求不转发 |\n| 后端超时 | 重试一次，失败返回 504 |\n| WebSocket 连接 | 长连接保持，双向通信正常 |\n\n### 7.4 测试覆盖率目标\n\n| 组件 | 目标覆盖率 |\n|------|-----------|\n| server.go | 80% |\n| backend.go | 85% |\n| route.go | 85% |\n| proxy.go | 80% |\n| health.go | 85% |\n| informer.go | 80% |\n| auth.go | 90% |\n| ratelimit.go | 90% |\n| metrics.go | 85% |\n\n---\n\n## 8. 关键接口定义\n\n### 8.1 Router 接口\n\n```go\ntype Router interface {\n    // Start begins serving HTTP requests\n    Start() error\n\n    // Stop gracefully shuts down the router\n    Stop(ctx context.Context) error\n\n    // AddBackend adds a backend to the pool\n    AddBackend(key, endpoint, pathPrefix, name string) error\n\n    // RemoveBackend removes a backend from the pool\n    RemoveBackend(key string)\n\n    // GetConfig returns current configuration\n    GetConfig() *Config\n\n    // GetMetrics returns current metrics\n    GetMetrics() *Metrics\n}\n```\n\n### 8.2 ServiceDiscoverer 接口\n\n```go\ntype ServiceDiscoverer interface {\n    // Start starts the informer\n    Start() error\n\n    // Stop stops the informer\n    Stop()\n\n    // GetEndpoint returns endpoint for given namespace and name\n    GetEndpoint(namespace, name, kind string) (string, error)\n}\n```\n\n### 8.3 ProxyHandler 接口\n\n```go\ntype ProxyHandler interface {\n    // ServeHTTP proxies the request to backend\n    ServeHTTP(w http.ResponseWriter, r *http.Request, backend *Backend)\n\n    // GetTransport returns the underlying HTTP transport\n    GetTransport() *http.Transport\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 9. 监控指标\n\n### 9.1 Prometheus 指标\n\n| Metric | Type | Labels | Description |\n|--------|------|--------|-------------|\n| `router_request_duration_seconds` | Histogram | method, path, backend | Request duration |\n| `router_backend_requests_total` | Counter | backend, status | Backend request count |\n| `router_backend_healthy` | Gauge | backend | Backend health status (1/0) |\n| `router_errors_total` | Counter | type | Error count by type |\n| `router_rate_limit_rejected_total` | Counter | client_ip | Rate limited requests |\n| `router_active_connections` | Gauge | backend | Active connections per backend |\n| `router_informer_sync_total` | Counter | resource_type | Informer sync count |\n\n### 9.2 健康检查端点\n\n- `/health/live` — Liveness probe (always returns 200 if process is running)\n- `/health/ready` — Readiness probe (returns 200 only if informers are synced and backend pool is initialized)\n\n---\n\n## 10. 实施计划\n\n### Phase 1: 核心功能\n- [ ] 完善 Router 主结构\n- [ ] 实现 BackendPool 的线程安全操作\n- [ ] 实现基础代理转发\n\n### Phase 2: Kubernetes 集成\n- [ ] 实现 Informer 完整功能\n- [ ] 集成 client-go 进行 CRD 监听\n- [ ] 实现 Add/Update/Delete 事件处理\n\n### Phase 3: 会话管理\n- [ ] 实现 JWT Token 生成和验证\n- [ ] 实现会话状态追踪\n- [ ] 实现基于 session 的路由\n\n### Phase 4: 可靠性\n- [ ] 完善健康检查逻辑\n- [ ] 实现熔断机制\n- [ ] 添加超时控制\n\n### Phase 5: 可观测性\n- [ ] 完善日志结构化\n- [ ] 添加完整 Prometheus 指标\n- [ ] 实现健康检查端点\n\n---\n\n## 11. 依赖\n\n### 11.1 外部依赖\n\n| Package | Version | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|---------|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | ^1.9.0 | HTTP framework |\n| `github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5` | ^5.0.0 | JWT token handling |\n| `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` | ^1.16.0 | Metrics |\n| `golang.org/x/time/rate` | ^0.5.0 | Rate limiting |\n| `k8s.io/client-go` | ^0.34.0 | Kubernetes client |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery` | ^0.34.0 | API types |\n| `k8s.io/klog/v2` | ^2.100.0 | Logging |\n\n### 11.2 内部依赖\n\n| Module | Purpose |\n|--------|---------|\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` | Generated Kubernetes typed client |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | CRD types |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/listers` | Resource listers |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/informers` | Shared informers |\n\n---\n\n## 12. 参考\n\n- [AR-009: Router HTTP 反向代理核心](design.md)\n- [Session Routing Design](session-routing/design.md)\n- [client-go library](deployment/client-go.md)\n- [Kubernetes Informer Pattern](https://medium.com/@cloud_eng/kubernetes-informers-the-magic-behind-operator-frameworks-2c4e3a87a9c3)","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/